{"body": "<div id=\"doc-contents\" class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1>ScalingMetric object</h1>\n  <p></p>\n\n\n\n\n    <h2>Example JSON representation</h2>\n    <pre><code>{\n  \"filePath\": \"string\", \n  \"function\": \"average\", \n  \"inverted\": true, \n  \"name\": \"string\", \n  \"retrieveMethod\": \"read\", \n  \"scope\": \"scalr\"\n}</code></pre>\n\n\n  <h2>Properties</h2>\n  <table class=\"fullwidth\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>property</th>\n        <th>attributes</th>\n        <th>valid values</th>\n        <th>description</th>\n        <th>filter option</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">filePath</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            string\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip required\">required</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">function</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            string\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip required\">required</span><br>\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip filterable\">filterable</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n            \"average\"<br/>\"sum\"<br/>\"min\"<br/>\"max\"\n        </td>\n        <td><p>Aggregate function to use when executing decision logic.</p></td>\n        <td>\n            ?function=...\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">name</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            string\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip required\">required</span><br>\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip filterable\">filterable</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>\n            ?name=...\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">retrieveMethod</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            string\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip required\">required</span><br>\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip filterable\">filterable</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n            \"read\"<br/>\"execute\"<br/>\"url-request\"\n        </td>\n        <td><p>The operation that should be performed on the File to obtain the value of the Metric.</p></td>\n        <td>\n            ?retrieveMethod=...\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">scope</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            string\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip read-only\">read-only</span><br>\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip filterable\">filterable</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n            \"scalr\"<br/>\"account\"<br/>\"environment\"<br/>\"farm\"<br/>\"farmrole\"<br/>\"role\"<br/>\"server\"\n        </td>\n        <td></td>\n        <td>\n            ?scope=...\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td><span class=\"fixed-width\">inverted</span><br/><span class=\"data-type\">\n            boolean\n        </span></td>\n        <td><span class=\"notes\">\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip optional\">optional</span><br>\n            <span class=\"need-tooltip filterable\">filterable</span><br>\n        </span></td>\n        <td>\n        </td>\n        <td><p>Whether this metric should be inverted. By default Farm Roles scale up when the value goes above the scale up threshold. If this is true, Farm Roles will scale up when the value goes below the scale up threshold.</p></td>\n        <td>\n            ?inverted=...\n        </td>      \n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <h2>Endpoints using this object</h2>\n  <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/user/scaling-metrics/post.html\">User / Scaling Metrics: Create</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/user/scaling-metrics/get.html\">User / Scaling Metrics: List</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/user/scaling-metrics/delete_metricName.html\">User / Scaling Metrics: Delete</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/user/scaling-metrics/get_metricName.html\">User / Scaling Metrics: Get</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/user/scaling-metrics/patch_metricName.html\">User / Scaling Metrics: Edit</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(function () {\n  var descriptions = {\n    \"required\": \"<i>Required</i> properties must be set when you send a <i>ScalingMetric</i> object to the API.\",\n    \"optional\": \"You can choose wether or not to set <i>Optional</i> properties when sending <i>ScalingMetric</i> objects to Scalr.\",\n    \"create-only\": \"<i>Create-only</i> properties are set when the object is created, but can't be modified later. They are typically allowed in POST requests but not in PATCH requests.\",\n    \"read-only\": \"<i>Read-only</i> properties are set by Scalr and can't be modified through the API. They are set when you retrieve a <i>ScalingMetric</i> from Scalr, but you should not set them when sending <i>ScalingMetric</i> objects to Scalr through POST or PATCH requests.\",\n    \"filterable\": \"<i>Filterable</i> properties can be used to filter the results returned by the API according to the value of these properties.\"\n  };\n  var spans = document.querySelectorAll('.need-tooltip');\n  for (var i = 0; i < spans.length; i ++) {\n    for (var cls in descriptions) {\n      var span = spans.item(i);\n      if ($(span).hasClass(cls)) {\n        new Tooltip({\n          target: span,\n          content: descriptions[cls],\n          classes: 'tooltip-theme-arrows',\n          position: 'top left'\n        });\n        break;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n});\n</script>\n", "title": "ScalingMetric definition - Scalr API Documentation"}